	,SRC_fact_result.RESULT_UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS RESULT_UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_fact_result.RESULT_UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS RESULT_UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY

        ,SRC_dim_user.USER_ID

	 FROM 
	$DO_TEMP_MY_MYSQL_FACT_RESULT SRC_fact_result   force index (fact_result_test_id_idx)
     join dim_user SRC_dim_user on SRC_fact_result.USER_KEY = SRC_dim_user.USER_KEY 
    where 
SRC_fact_result.test_id>0
and STR_TO_DATE(CAST( SRC_fact_result.result_created_at_date_key  AS CHAR(8)),'%Y%m%d')> DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL $SP_LOOK_BACK_DAYS.look_back_days DAY )


-- AND SRC_fact_result.user_key=17019731 (used in test cases for deduping)
-- and SRC_dim_user.is_current=1

attributes.attrExprVal: DI_CF(trim(cast(SRC_dim_program.PROGRAM_ID as char(255))) + '|' + trim(cast( SRC_fact_result.TEST_ID  as char(255))))

ROW_NUMBER() OVER 
(
PARTITION BY
	PIDs.V_PERSON_PID ,PIDs.V_INTERVENTION_PID ,PIDs.V_OFFERING_PID ,PIDs.V_TEST_PID 
ORDER BY
       PIDs.V_PERSON_PID ,PIDs.V_INTERVENTION_PID ,PIDs.V_OFFERING_PID ,PIDs.V_TEST_PID , SRC_fact_result.V_ENTERED_AT_DATE desc, SRC_fact_result.ENTERED_AT_TIME_KEY desc
)
case when SRC_dim_person.PERSON_KEY is null then -1 else SRC_dim_person.PERSON_KEY end
case when SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_KEY is null then -1 else SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_KEY end
case when SRC_dim_offering.OFFERING_KEY is null then -1 else SRC_dim_offering.OFFERING_KEY end
case when SRC_dim_test.TEST_KEY is null then -1 else SRC_dim_test.TEST_KEY end

dCmd_Inst.dCmd:
UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'SUCCEEDED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
SRC_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_result.SourceCount    , 
SRC_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_result.ProcessCount  , 
SRC_target_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_result.TargetCount  , 
SRC_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_result.BadCount  ,
TGT_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_outcomes.SourceCount   , 
TGT_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_outcomes.ProcessCount  , 
TGT_target_count  =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_outcomes.TargetCount   , 
TGT_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_outcomes.BadCount   ,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'FAILED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'

INSERT INTO control_load_history (data_flow_name, status, start_timestamp, created_at)
VALUES ('DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS', 'RUNNING', $$CurrentTimeStamp, $$CurrentTimeStamp);

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'ABORTED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_outcomes_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING';
